➜Ella个人首演压力大到流泪 称对演艺圈又爱又恨
http://www.sohu.com/a/429380159_99962390	8070
<p><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201104/fdf3d11cccd04010a214c9bb46b963ea.jpeg" /></p>
